ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce du Grand Mont-Tremblant - Quebec ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DU GRAND MONT-TREMBLANT, in Quebec, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES of its district from the municipalities of Brébeuf, La Conception, Mont-Tremblant, Saint-Faustin-Lac-Carré and Lac Supérieur to Brébeuf, La Conception, Mont-Tremblant, Saint-Faustin-Lac-Carré, Lac Supérieur and Amherst.
